Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result of pride, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys don't know about themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing more terrifying than obliviousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave it to me, Superbia...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avaritia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:23.16,EP-Title,Typeset,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8\fscx80\fscy80\fad(486,0)\t(0,1028,\blur0\fscx100\fscy100\shad3)\t(1029,1030,\bord0.1)\t(1653,3989,\shad12\blur5)\pos(625,514)}The Time of Disasters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry. I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tired, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to call my mom... {my mother / She literally just says "to my mother"}{when reverseness is unavoidable, just tl it full ~MMC}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're in this world{dimension}, we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one to protect you, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly, I'll be the one to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
