Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.48,11eyes - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H273438&\fs45\fscx200\pos(657,557)}Where's Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's sleeping in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she's lost her stamina. {literally "broke her health"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka is sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all just take a break today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be dangerous to go into the Crimson Night separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:44.91,11eyes - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H273438&\fs25\fscx160\pos(977,697)\frx324\fry0}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.03,11eyes - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H273438&\fs25\fscx160\frx348\fry0\pos(975,660)}Yes
