Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but can you pour some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure can use that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to win if we use that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that means we'll also be powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To win, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that we should win against?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do to end this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be swallowed by the Crimson Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put an end to the black knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we do is fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to protect ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They keep attacking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "fragment" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than the six of us being students, we have nothing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the "sin" that the black knights speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight 'cause they attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing to do in a fight is win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being distressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The one who awoke the demon is you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please don't hurt Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:43.48,Type Set Customized,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\c&H273438&\fs75\fscx120\frz33.2\move(245,589,427,532,0,3698)}I have no \N\N\N\N\N\N\h   memory of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm checking our barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's surrounding the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a demon comes, it'll react.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this world safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you sense it with your powers as an Onmyouji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that isn't something to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was during a fight. You couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, it's his fault for going around all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep worrying about something like that, \Nyou won't be able to win a battle you would have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First comes winning. Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he died there, that means it would've been his fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happened, he'd be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that how you've been living up 'til now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've survived, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen many deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even people I loved very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've died in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It breaks my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...another side of me surfaces...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make any more friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That it was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For friends and for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the crimson night, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I've made more friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met people who accept who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really love everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... That's why I didn't want to hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone anymore, Takahisa-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being protected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember ever being...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is Saeko-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's... not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She used both Eastern and Western skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a forbidden incantation called the "Gehou."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventy years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Onmyouji that was expelled for using that "Gehou"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was Kusakabe Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a woman who can cast high-level incantations.{my best guess "take utsu shita jutsu wo tsukai"}{takuitsu shita jujutsu tsukai de atta Misao ~MMC}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was investigating her, I found myself looking up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong, noble woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings for her still haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Knight called Superbia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is Kusakabe Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why she's in the Crimson Night and why she's a Black Knight, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she is, without a doubt, Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... That's just weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person called Misao was from seventy years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she already dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no concept of time in the Crimson Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have noticed this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After crossing over, no matter how much time passes, when you return it's the same instant as when you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world where the stream of time is halted, Misao Kusakabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has continued to live to seventy years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And became a Black Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mark of one that has used "Gehou".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right before the beginning of the Crimson Night,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had been struck by a mysterious wind while I was divining a fortune and was branded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person I admire now stands before me as an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, it is a fact that the difference in power was proven last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, she's not an opponent I can possibly face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, I'll entrust the powers of Kusakabe to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also for Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I have been reduced to a witch of time, I still have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This burning feeling I have for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This love without falsehood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world that you despised so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world that stole your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely... definitely erase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crud!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.02,11eyes - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz14.367\c&H77706C&\fs40\frx342\fry8\pos(657,361)\b1}Infirmary{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure has the best aroma when it's just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I gonna hear your lecture again here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you came prepared for {\i1}lectures{\i0}. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over at a friend's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend? Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I have to report it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had any issues, the person responsible would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. It's that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The petite and cute girl with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see, I see. That's what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's fine. You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's youth for ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been seven years since I've picked you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's passed, it sure seems fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things like "picked up."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an object.
