Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll go to class and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Come by after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's payday, so I'll treat you to some grilled meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grilled meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just sleep a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stomach will hurt if you eat grilled meat after staying up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{Blah blah blah... this is why I hate school. teachers make no sense}{asa POWER: あしたに死し、ゆふべに生るゝならひ}Some die in the morning; others are born in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{Blah blah blah... this is why I hate school. teachers make no sense}{asa POWER: たゞ水の泡にぞ似たりける}Alive: they are like those bubbles floating on the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{more blah blah blah}{asa POWER: 知らず、生れ死ぬる人、いづかたより來りて、いづかたへか去る}Nor is it clear to me, as people are born and die, where they are coming from and where they are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think's happened to Yuka and Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{zZzZzZz}{Asa POWER: 又知らず、かりのやどり、誰が爲に心を惱まし、何によりてか目をよろこばしむる。}Nor why, being so ephemeral in this world, they take such pains to make their houses pleasing to the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a flying love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-chan. Please accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{*POP* huh? ooh, a flying airplane! zZzZzZz}{asa power: そのあるじとすみかと、無常をあらそひ去るさま}The master and the dwelling are competing in their transience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{*POP* huh? ooh, a flying airplane! zZzZzZz}{asa power: いはゞ朝顏の露にことならず。}Both will perish from this world like the morning glory that blooms in the morning dew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A love air mail. From: Tadashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooooo~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teruya! You got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My love-love air mail was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! We're still in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We were?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? What is it, Momono?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling a little sick, so I'm going to go to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Are you all right on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I'll go on a date with Shiori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'll accompany Shiori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess this means that I can't ignore this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, that's some good movement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body feels light. I can also see her movements clearly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From the side, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well. It's all thanks to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuka!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm just like Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up talking to Satchii...{nanka Sachi to katari tsuichatta}{reference from Dennou Coil ~MMC}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to cheer me up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even so, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeko-sensei is... Well, I can't really put it it into words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We actually take the people close to us for granted more than we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only figured it out {\i1}after{\i0} they were gone. {I believe she's talking about the lonesomeness that had taken over her before}{it's not inakunatte ha kattandesu, it's inakunatte wakattandesu ~MMC}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who were always there for and with me had suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like a wide hole had opened up inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I had been supported."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I had been protected."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thanks for the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have not noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you {\i1}gone,{\i0} too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had it pretty bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause right now, you're in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure are petite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've been fighting so hard, despite your size.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:19:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saeko, if you hadn't picked me up, I wouldn't be here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I probably wouldn't even be alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once the Crimson Night ends, let's go touring somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You, me, and Yukiko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet it'll be fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go search a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, that Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her so many times not to move around so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she comes back, be sure to let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to resemble his older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably can't communicate with you too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can help, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk with Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with the sudden cleaning frenzy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're freeloaders here. We should at least clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now this is the Yuka I'm used to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a gecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of lizards...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's not poisonous, and it protects the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't attack or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it bothers you, I'll catch it and bring it out... {outside/ he doesn't complete his sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, you're warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:21:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if it were always just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they found Yukiko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything were to happen to you, I'd use my powers and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to use your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Do you hate me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you use your powers, you become tired, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to suffer any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go check the second floor. Stay here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once the Crimson Night ends, everything will be back to normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it ever does...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that happens, Yuka will surely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened. There's a draft going through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting, Master of the Aeon's Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori...-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{*TLC*}I've been sent by the Holy Ministry of the Index Librorum Prohibitorum.{禁書目録聖省 ~MMC}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Shiori Momono. My true name is Summoner Ursula.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because you have awoken the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,648)}It'd be nice if the Crimson Night doesn't come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.27,0:24:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it really all right for me to come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Saeko's payday is everyone's payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean! But I'll come along since you said so.{loosely TLed}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Eat up, eat up! Eat it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.11,0:24:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I've had grilled meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.84,0:24:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.19,0:24:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sae...ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.92,0:24:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Broken Bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.89,0:24:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, the two of them lived happily ever after.
